sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Mind
    participant CX as Cortex
    participant HP as Hippocampus
    participant SL as Salience
    participant SY as Synapse

    C->>CX: store_memory
    CX->>HP: StoreCommand
    HP->>HP: Validate, assign tier, persist
    HP-->>SL: MemoryStored
    HP-->>SY: MemoryStored
    SL->>SL: Set initial salience score
    SY->>SY: Create associations from metadata
    HP-->>CX: Acknowledgment
    CX-->>C: MCP tool response
